definitions.definition: A village in Westerleigh parish, South Gloucestershire district, Gloucestershire , England ( OS grid ref ST693822 ) .
An unincorporated community in Union County , Oregon , United States .
A city in Cache County , Utah , United States .
A habitational surname from Old English .
